          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Alternatives to Opioids Prescribing Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services (CMS) to carry out a demonstration project to evaluate alternatives to&nbsp;the use of&nbsp;opioids to treat Medicare enrollees&nbsp;in hospital emergency departments. Under the project, the CMS must provide incentive payments to&nbsp;participating hospitals&nbsp;for decreasing the use of opioids and increasing the use of opioid alternatives. <br /><b><b><b></b></b></b></p><b><b></b></b>]]></text>
